==Definition==

<b>compass</b> (<i>noun</i>)
# A magnetic or electronic device used to determine the cardinal directions (usually [[magnetic_north]])
# A tool used to draw circles in geometry, carpentry, manufacture, etc...
:([[beam_compass]])
# (circular path?)
: M. Le Page Du Pratz, <i>History of Louisisana</i> (PG), p. 47
:: <i>In going up the Missisippi, we meet with nothing remarkable before we come to the Detour aux Anglois, the English Reach: in that part the river takes a large <b>compass</b>;</i>

